_sText:
This is my first map.
Please let me know what you think :D

This is only beta version,
I can add more stuff if someone can add any suggestions!

Enjoy.



How to install:

add to 

C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\YOUR_USERNAME\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps


Note:

If you see pink and black checkered boxes it means you're missing textures.
You may need the following textures:

Skybox - http://www.gamebanana.com/textures/2870

Neon Textures - http://www.gamebanana.com/textures/1315

Dev Textures - http://www.gamebanana.com/textures/


Thanks to the authors of the textures
